{"tid":220486,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"都話左肥係一種罪孽嚟嫁啦","createTime":"2017-04-28T03:32:37.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-28T03:32:37.000Z","uid":13495,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"cbb2c5fa3134c9e8e841c37f4d6baf1c102ff01a","tid":220486,"uid":13495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T03:32:37.000Z","msg":"美國俄亥俄州一間殯儀館發生離奇意外，職員火化一具癡肥遺體時，火勢突然變猛，更擴散至火化爐外釀成火警；幸事件中無人受傷，火勢亦未波及其他屍體。<br />\n<br />\n大火發生在周二晚，殯儀館負責人卡奇恩（Don Catchen）指，火化期間火勢變得強勁，令大火擴散至火化爐外，並燒著一個火化箱，「那具遺體屬癡肥，火化過程明顯比一般的更熱」。<br />\n<br />\n消防員表示幸火葬場做足防火措施，成功阻止火勢蔓延，事件沒人受傷，亦未有波及其他屍體。<br />\n<br />\n業內人士指火化癡肥遺體有危險，是因為會出現俗稱「油脂火」，維珍尼亞州2014年火化一具500磅遺體時亦曾發生火警；奧地利在2012年火化一具440磅的女屍時亦引發火燭，令消防員「覆蓋着一層烏黑油脂」。<br />\n<br />\n英國《都巿報》/《每日鏡報》<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170428&amp;guid=56621060&amp;category_guid=10793140&amp;category=instant\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170428%26guid%3D56621060%26category_guid%3D10793140%26category%3Dinstant&d=%2F2JumwqaKkMO2nYek6mTvZnkJiu3DM%2BvEze6mtExKRo%3D&h=739af3c5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170428%26guid%3D56621060%26category_guid%3D10793140%26category%3Dinstant&h=ddaf42cc\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170428&amp;guid=56621060&amp;category_guid=10793140&amp;category=instant</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}